codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Italia ~ Eurōpā est; Graecia ~ in Eurōpā est. Choose from this set of possible answers [ in quoque, et, ne nōn, Ubi, sed, nōn sed, fluvius] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'in quoque', 'et', 'ne nōn', 'Ubi', 'sed', 'nōn sed', 'fluvius']
